    "title": "助言する権利をあげる！",
    "enTitle": "You May Advise Me!",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日、トレーニングコースで――",
            "enText": "One day, at the training track...",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "pathId": -8957298783820906537,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングヘイロー",
            "enName": "King Halo",
            "jpText": "ちょっと、そこのあなた！",
            "enText": "Hey! You there!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "voiceIdx": 52,
            "voiceSheetId": "051061001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -8302430360366187451
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -5802269528254042954
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7296173670100619010,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングヘイロー",
            "enName": "King Halo",
            "jpText": "さっきからいい指導をしてるじゃない。\r\n見ているポイントが的確。",
            "enText": "I've been observing you, and based on<n>what I've\nseen, your advice is not only<n>sound, but also\nhighly effective.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 6145456050468706917
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 2888681104941171303
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3480673691379264584,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングヘイロー",
            "enName": "King Halo",
            "jpText": "だから特別に私にアドバイスをする権利を\r\nあげる。さ、身になる話を1分で済ませて？",
            "enText": "As such, I shall honor you with the<n>special\nprivilege of giving me advice.<n>You have one\nminute to tell me<n>something useful.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": 61,
            "voiceSheetId": "051061001",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "こっちもトレーニング中なんだけど……",
                    "enText": "But I'm in the middle of training too...",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 3110159270005931746
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 415106886981656593
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6512936383850883613,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングヘイロー",
            "enName": "King Halo",
            "jpText": "あら。このキングとディベート\r\nできるなんて滅多にない機会よ？",
            "enText": "Oh? It's not often you get the<n>opportunity to\nexchange words with<n>someone as illustrious as\nme, you know!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "voiceSheetId": "051061001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 529867819000366762
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 2881169406933835405
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3780851898416273524,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングヘイロー",
            "enName": "King Halo",
            "jpText": "その機会を逃すなんて……\r\nあるまじき行動だと思わない？",
            "enText": "It would be rather foolish of you not to<n>take\nadvantage of such a chance.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 5822156599051308827
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -2558855428333040508
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5097148520517573292,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "なにかアドバイスをするまで彼女から\r\n解放されなさそうだ。それなら――",
            "enText": "It looks like she's not going to let me go<n>unless I\ngive her some kind of advice, so<n>I try to think of\nsomething to say.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "昨今の根性論について討論する",
                    "enText": "What do you think of the saying \"Where there's\na will, there's a way\"?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "仕掛けるタイミングについて話す",
                    "enText": "Any thoughts on timing your strategy in a race?",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 6402719788362715430
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 143,
                    "pathId": -6563965313499177958
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3812463045270946854,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングヘイロー",
            "enName": "King Halo",
            "jpText": "へぇ……いいわね。\r\nその内容は、確かに興味があるわ。",
            "enText": "Oh? What an intriguing question. I must<n>say, it\nmakes for a fine discussion point.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "voiceSheetId": "051061001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -5913762843915536712
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 5546738583558982915
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4685066115607163968,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そしてキングヘイローとしばらく話し合った。",
            "enText": "And so, King Halo and I discuss the<n>topic for a\nwhile.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 6771215023859415816
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": 554915304357045078
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5185751487380180063,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングヘイロー",
            "enName": "King Halo",
            "jpText": "……あら、着眼点は悪くないわね。\r\n仕掛けと言えば末脚！",
            "enText": "Ah, I appreciate your subject of choice.<n>Timing is\ncritical when making a final<n>spurt in the\nhomestretch!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "voiceSheetId": "051061001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -5213623960857764878
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 2294150055112106125
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6441943265103065561,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングヘイロー",
            "enName": "King Halo",
            "jpText": "そして、このキングの武器も末脚！\r\nさあお互いに、語り合いましょう！",
            "enText": "And it's that very skill that serves as my<n>ultimate\nweapon! Allow me to tell you<n>all about it!",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "voiceSheetId": "051061001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 3178601549013624957
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": 1803437956602712883
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5377781544424760115,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そしてキングヘイローとしばらく話し合った。",
            "enText": "And so, King Halo and I discuss the<n>topic for a\nwhile.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
