            "pathId": -442897143780297179,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングヘイロー",
            "enName": "King Halo",
            "jpText": "あら、もうこんな時間なの？\r\nそれじゃ、失礼するわね。",
            "enText": "Goodness, look at the time! I must be<n>going now.",
